Guvf vf Gnfx 14 bs gur Rhqlcghyn Punyyratr
------------------------------------------

Abj gung lbh unir gur onfvpf bs yvfgf, naq jr tybffrq bire gur phfgbz
nyybpngbef (gur svefg phg ng gung gnfx jnf zhpu uneqre, lbh tbg bss
rnfl), vg'f gvzr gb zbir ba gb fbzrguvat n ovg zber byq-fpubby: gnfxf.

Sbe guvf gnfx:
  - Nqq n arj svryq gb gur pber xreary gnfx fgehpgher pnyyrq, jnvg sbe
    vg, "vq".
  - Jura gur gnfx vf perngrq, frg gur vq gb lbhe vq.  Vzntvangvir, V
    xabj.  Lbh gel jevgvat gurfr gnfxf.
  - Nqq n arj cebp svyr sbe rirel gnfx pnyyrq, "vq", ybpngrq va gur
    /cebp/${CVQ}/ qverpgbel sbe gung gnfx.
  - Jura gur cebp svyr vf ernq sebz, unir vg cevag bhg gur inyhr bs
    lbhe vq, naq gura vaperzrag vg ol bar, nyybjvat qvssrerag gnfxf gb
    unir qvssrerag inyhrf sbe gur "vq" svyr bire gvzr nf gurl ner ernq
    sebz.
  - Cebivqr fbzr "cebbs" vg nyy jbexf cebcreyl.

Nf lbh ner gbhpuvat svyrf nyy bire gur xreary gerr, n cngpu vf gur
erdhverq erfhyg gb or frag va urer.  Cyrnfr fcrpvsl juvpu xreary irefvba
lbh znxr guvf cngpu ntnvafg, gb tvir zl iveghny znpuvarf n punapr gb
svther bhg ubj gb nccyl vg.

Nyfb cebivqr fbzr xvaq bs cebbs gung lbh grfgrq gur cngpu.

Naq, va pnfr lbh unccrarq gb sbetrg vg, lbhe vq vf "5q658q788pp9".
